Q_DESC:
Create a class called Complement. The class has private integer data member named number. 
Include the following functions: 
setData() to provide initial value to the data member 
getData() that returns the value of the number 
findNinescomplement() that calculates and returns the 9s complement of the number 
findTenscomplement() that calculates and returns the 10s complement of the number 
In the main method, create an object of the Complement class and invoke the different methods. 
Input and Output Format : 
Input consists of a single integer. 
Refer sample input and output for formatting specifications. 
All text in bold corresponds to input and the rest corresponds to output
